array.item: The adventures of a new generation of Warner Bros. Looney Tunes characters.
A boy named Bobby Generic creates adventures using his overactive imagination
The Dark Knight battles crime in Gotham City with occasional help from Robin and Batgirl.

Two demoted fighter pilots battle evil as high flying masked vigilantes.
